import React from 'react';
import { Nav, Navbar, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';

function NavBar() {
    return (
        
            <Row>
                <Col>
                <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="md"  style={{ background: 'url(http://www.getmdl.io/assets/demos/transparent.jpg) center / cover' }}>
                    <Navbar.Brand href="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', }}>My Portfolio</Navbar.Brand>
                
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
               
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                        <Nav className="mr-auto">
                            <Nav.Link href="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', }}>Home</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', }}>Link</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', }}>Link</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', }}>Link</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', }}>Link</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
             
                </Navbar>
       
           </Col>
     </Row>
    )
}
export default NavBar;
